{"tid":127484,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"輿論圍剿雲加 哥帥：不能接受！","createTime":"2017-02-20T06:32:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T08:05:45.000Z","uid":46892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16ab011bbfd2c3fceb6819b690b3dc5a3b25b76c","tid":127484,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=qB%2BEr1lTQcBPVU2CyFsNoghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9d4c5da6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】阿仙奴於歐聯16強首回合大敗給拜仁1:5，令外界對領隊雲加離隊的呼聲更為熾熱，為兵工廠競爭對手的曼城領隊哥迪奧拿卻出言維護雲加，指外界的輿論是不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴近年成績停滯不前，10年來只有兩座英足盃冠軍落袋，加上近期球隊狀態低迷，現年67歲的領隊雲加（Arsene Wenger）再度成為外界輿論圍剿的目標，傳媒謠傳前者季末退休不在話下，連兵工廠名宿基昂也暗示雲加是時候離隊，沒想到這時候為雲加雪中送炭的竟是曼城領隊哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）。<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿對外界胡亂猜測雲加的未來感到非常不滿，他被問及下周二對哈特斯菲爾德會否改變陣容時，狠批道：「在過去的10天，我聽到市民、舊球員和傳媒，如何對雲加做出不能接受的行為；球隊正值低潮的時候，領隊從來不會得到尊重，雖然無禮，但事實就是如此，所以每當我們做決定，外界就可以隨心所欲作評論。」<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴周一將出戰英足盃第5圈作客非聯賽球隊瑟頓聯，而曼城則備戰周二主場對摩納哥的歐聯16強首回合賽事。"},{"pid":"288ad73b0d81c385172fa6c9715cedc98047b67d","tid":127484,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:35:19.000Z","msg":"哥狗都是迷雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aefe5c628cc77187d48c3c0637c49dfa1f17a1c","tid":127484,"uid":34513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:39:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哥狗都是迷雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔留住條死老野點樣每季拎硬6分啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83cf6f81718eca109c80b6075ca5a16283b9ab1f","tid":127484,"uid":81569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T07:50:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哥狗都是迷雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔留住條死老野點樣每季拎硬6分啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦ching<br />\n鏝作客阿妓 基本上輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4a469273ad5915c332d012813124646de9853c","tid":127484,"uid":435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:02:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哥狗都是迷雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔留住條死老野點樣每季拎硬6分啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦ching<br />\n鏝作客阿妓 基本上輸硬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪玩啦ching<br />\n2月既阿記連南華都踢唔贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c74a6ae0f7148dc75367be922964e5b28f36f51","tid":127484,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/160542_19d610c634d93baa49c353d114ec2be9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F160542_19d610c634d93baa49c353d114ec2be9.jpg&h=ed2a0bb5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}